2.Gradient.xml
XML Code:

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<shape xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
<gradient android:angle="250" android:startColor="@color/colorGrey" android:endColor="#FFFF00"/>
</shape>







3.Ripple_number.xml
XML Code:


<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ripple xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:color="#573F3F">
<item>
    <shape android:shape="rectangle">
        <solid android:color="@color/colorBrown"/>
    </shape>
</item>
</ripple>

4.Ripple_operations.xml
XML Code:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ripple xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:color="#777777">
    <item>
        <shape android:shape="rectangle">
            <solid android:color="@color/colorBlue"/>

        </shape>

    </item>
</ripple>

5.Red_button.xml
XML Code:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<selector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
<item
    android:state_pressed="false"
    android:state_enabled="true"
    android:drawable="@drawable/gradient_effect">
</item>
</selector>
